            "title": "群創南科五廠售予日月光半導體 預計處分利益約133億元",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"214\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/rQo9DBMWF1efE68cgMUwxA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTcwNTtoPTM5Nw--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/cnyes_hk_559/4bfab6ba2355faa45c6f0d763917aea9\" width=\"380\"/></div></figure></div>",
